abilities.name: Synchronize
abilities.description: If the OHKO move is used on another Pokémon while an OHKO target is adjacent to Mew, it will Paralyze the current target, but during the no-moves turn this Mew chooses two random direct moves at the same time, one of them never having hit a normal target before and the other having missed one a turn previously.

abilities.name: Telepathy
abilities.description: No secondary effects can affect Mew due to another Pokémon's moves.
